replies.body:
Totally sucks now, that 20% slow is nothing against tenacity/swiftness mastery/swiftness boots, its like its not even there. All the hype about getting it early is just that, pointless hype, you get it earlier with a passive that basically no longer exists against champs you actually need it for, aka brain dead tankmasters with 600 movespeed that cant be slowed.

So what you're left with in the end is a 25% less stats Rylai with a passive that basically doesnt exist vs summoners with the above mentioned combination of items/masteries, all that for a 600g cost reduction....worth it? Fuck no
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
